<div id="about" class="container splash-text">
  <h2 class="subtitle">About Micah:</h2>
  Micah is based on an excel spreadsheet system used by Micah [insert_last_name]. It spoke to me when I saw it because
  it incorporates elements of GTD methodology (Getting Things Done, an organizational framework), but in a way that
  combines all aspects of GTD into the same place: lists, projects, next actions, and steps. It even includes a way
  to "comment" on the project, giving status updates that file in horizontally in a date-ordered format, so that you
  always see the most recent update.
  <br /><br />
  In sum, a simple way to visualize your projects, the associated tasks, and date-ordered status updates, all in one place.
