<div id="tasks" class="container splash-text">
  <h2 class="subtitle">Micah's tasks:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Add a 'project', a place where you'd like to keep related tasks.</li>
    <br />
    <li>Add tasks/goals to the project. You can color-code them if you'd like.</li>
    <br />
    <li>For each task/goal, add all the relevant steps, which appear to the right as a checklist.</li>
    <br />
    <li>Add status updates as you go. Check off the steps as you complete them.</li>
    <br />
    <li>Mark tasks as done when all steps are complete. Completed tasks/steps will appear below the incomplete ones.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
